        "title": "feat(nebius): add direct SSH lease provider",
        "body": "Closes https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/364\n\nRebuilds https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/pull/433 on current `main`. The contributor branch could not accept the required workflow-bearing maintainer update, so this keeps the contributor's work and co-authorship on a reviewed maintainer branch.\n\n## Summary\n\n- add the direct Nebius AI Cloud SSH lease provider, configuration, docs, registration, and guarded live smoke harness\n- create managed VMs through the authenticated Nebius CLI, inject per-lease SSH access with cloud-init, and preserve normal Crabbox sync/run/stop behavior\n- harden claim ownership, stale/concurrent mutation handling, rollback cleanup contexts, `--keep` failure recovery, identity validation, and secret-safe CLI failures\n- align command construction with official Nebius CLI 0.12.230: profile/platform/image discovery, managed boot disk arguments, delete syntax, and raw cloud-init string handling\n\n## Verification\n\n- `go test -race ./internal/providers/nebius ./internal/providers/all`\n- `go test -race ./...`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `npm run format:check --prefix worker`\n- `npm run lint --prefix worker`\n- `npm run check --prefix worker`\n- `npm test --prefix worker`\n- `npm run build --prefix worker`\n- `node --test scripts/live-nebius-smoke.test.js`\n- `scripts/check-docs.sh`\n- autoreview: clean after resolving lifecycle, compatibility, and pagination findings\n- official Nebius CLI 0.12.230 help surfaces checked locally for every mutating and discovery command\n\n## Live proof\n\n- tested head: `daad5da0`\n- command: `CRABBOX_LIVE=1 CRABBOX_LIVE_PROVIDERS=nebius scripts/live-nebius-smoke.sh`\n- result: pass on a real Nebius VM; doctor, complete inventory, provision, cloud-init readiness, SSH `echo ok`, status/list, release, cleanup dry-run, and final absence all passed\n- cleanup: Nebius inventory confirmed empty after release\n\n## Delegated Linux proof\n\n- provider: `blacksmith-testbox`\n- tested head: `6b04b87e`\n- lease: `tbx_01kvcvv8nsy4axk6qeg3hm928h` (`golden-prawn`)\n- command: `go test -race ./internal/providers/nebius ./internal/providers/all`\n- result: pass; delegated sync; clean automatic stop; exit 0\n",
